    "question": "Some people think that having a set retirement age (e.g. 65 years) for everybody, regardless of occupation is unfair. They believe that certain workers deserve to retire and receive a pension at an earlier age.\n\nDo you agree or disagree?\n\nWhich type of workers do you think should benefit from early retirement?",
